  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f1724ae9-9754-4101-a3d8-78e58c377cd5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d7e21541-6914-4e78-a190-6c9e95cc9834\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-beeb9b81-bb3c-45ff-b261-729550bad6a6\">안녕하세요 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a2411156-b9a8-4297-99ea-08a2a57f62ec\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8e2fd541-377d-4bfb-b287-7ee766a30965\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-739718e5-be0e-4004-8afb-798735a33563\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f786db96-997e-479f-932a-d24b9eb8d13e\">7호선 남성역 1번 출구 앞, 경희 ) 이수한의원 입니다 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6cf9f044-a27b-44e6-88a0-3952058625fa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a95584f8-7536-45f2-a5bc-6d698e99c624\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ee3055a4-6aae-422f-b044-4bc76b9e0cc2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1bfc4fb0-63ba-4bb2-83f3-dd556d7fb052\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e3aac27d-3390-4ab1-9073-aebd1ba26ee3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5256f13b-984d-4b39-bbcb-71dca24bb12d\">2021년에는 코로나가 좀 잠잠 해질 줄알았는데</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-958755e2-6431-4df6-b8ab-0d4347bbae2b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bd571e38-a855-4a19-8eab-4e74d1fe78b6\">진짜 며칠동안 계속 천명이 훨씬 넘고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bd36f000-9b8e-4bc1-803a-d77d25c48f28\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1cafcb5d-6c29-49cb-9681-3fa5fab33e67\">900 800 700 600 500 400 300... </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-62eb03c5-11be-49ce-8100-5274f019fc28\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-368a027b-dc9f-4956-999f-f704520dd294\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8adba3ec-db24-4aff-a1fc-469f4b40cf62\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8aab37c7-702a-48ae-a37d-c0b35725028b\">요즘은 300명 좀 넘던데</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7def45c1-10f3-4375-bb70-a260cac2b580\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2569a2bc-dfbc-4faf-9537-bfd52f507753\">얼른 하루빨리 0명이면 좋겠어요</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c6ed73fd-c840-4a55-852a-fe9cfc6a8867\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ceed8696-0eb6-4625-ad91-b9d191bcae6f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ce86fc72-69c4-4dc4-8291-25e06087bd07\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-88edf9a4-6bce-44ca-a2e3-423bfa63f9f1\">올해 소원 딱 한가지에요..</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-45f64b49-44b6-475b-9287-ec1a7007217f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-05e22ceb-0a3c-4d08-8532-9f76d5d53e10\">모든 확진자들이 완치되고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eb13ed85-c776-4bd0-9d12-2275a6644d2f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4b1e6b3f-018a-4b9c-90fe-07131b7a7ca0\">제발 코로나 좀 없어지게 해주세요 ㅜ </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cd5773e1-0ae3-4b4f-801a-a76b08462929\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-52c2b4d1-0651-4de6-ade6-aaf8eddfc562\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-28ae0537-e058-4fa4-a934-1ba75f50c57c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-007df2c2-d946-4c3a-aa18-39b3796986ff\">뉴</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-97496ea7-2242-46fb-855f-636b7880f234\">스 보니까 설연휴 기간동안에도 2.5 단계는 유지되면서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-191b91b5-96ed-4b08-ab27-bac272d68671\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f3f43cf3-0f4d-4fb7-b13f-4372df6aa9af\">같은 주소 가족이 아닐경우 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b4d70425-90a5-41dd-a0f2-499f69d0eef3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5c8e494b-bf3a-4915-89e6-51cfff12760a\">4인 이상 모임 금지라고 하던데..</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e2d7902e-5b29-4d9e-a786-61745355499a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dc147eb4-1aa1-4789-913c-508e52583cc5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-88639449-7ec7-4a59-ab5c-a4f2a8006b23\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8b703f25-8384-4123-b0cd-e682202dcc94\">작년 추석에도 시골에 못가고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0e4a8cff-77cc-41b1-b001-def1e0154b04\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9c8f623a-4767-41b5-934d-5cfcc1adf78d\">올해 설날에도 못가게 생겼어요</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-da00b816-5388-4d5d-b26a-cc12eab969b8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1a8cd8a3-e757-42de-bf31-5ac22c69a74a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-670a516f-fe84-45f5-add7-8581102fb192\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-48b21933-5740-4811-91e6-1af89ce6764b\">전화로 인사드려야할거같아요 ㅜㅜ</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7d3b87c3-4e25-4254-a0d3-973352ff6842\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-60c99d24-82ec-4a27-9d23-9aa6ead2bef7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aa95710f-364f-4652-989a-2de15d792350\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0d999c70-7171-4c3f-8508-a19d6d5a99f0\">가족들이랑 생이별 하는게.. 이렇게 힘드네요 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-624ef88c-3f95-4efd-901e-1d6a59b0d650\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-708f22f4-4644-40ec-b3c6-ef4d5f4a9ee2\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a306e3bd-5229-40c1-b6cb-f74b0a9049f8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9c877291-fb8e-4471-b725-6c31f45dcc47\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-al